These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Transport: van, subway, roller, car
Nationality: dutch, spanish, egyptian, thai
1. Transport:van is on the right of Nationality:egyptian##1
2. Nationality:thai is on the far left##1
3. Nationality:egyptian is between Nationality:spanish and Transport:subway##2
4. Transport:car is on the far left##1
5. Transport:roller is between Transport:subway and Transport:van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Transport   | car         | subway   | roller | van       |
| Nationality      | thai | dutch | egyptian   | spanish |

