.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Beverage: tea, fanta, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
Flower: poppy, amaryllis, balloon-flower, tulip
1. Flower:tulip is between Beverage:iced-tea and Flower:amaryllis##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
3. Flower:balloon-flower is on the right of Flower:poppy##1
4. Beverage:tea is on the left of Flower:poppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage         | fanta | tea | iced-tea | hot-chocolate |
| Flower   | amaryllis    | tulip   | poppy | balloon-flower       |

