.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
Color: fuchsia, blue, amber, red
Music-Genre: ambient, dubstep, jazz, blues
1. Music-Genre:jazz is on the right of Color:red##1
2. Music-Genre:jazz is between Music-Genre:dubstep and Color:blue##2
3. Music-Genre:dubstep is on the far left##1
4. Music-Genre:blues is on the left of Color:amber##1
5. Color:blue == Music-Genre:blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Color          | red    | fuchsia | blue   | amber  |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | jazz   | blues | ambient |

